column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId   FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL  SELECT u.up_name as [name],   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id
